lqWK-Vw1KYE.title: Slay It Don’t Spray It with Jay Pharoah, Nikki Glaser, Terry Crews and Dan Finnerty | That’s My Jam
lqWK-Vw1KYE.description:
Jay Pharoah, Nikki Glaser, Terry Crews and Dan Finnerty try to dodge a booth bath while performing "Get the Party Started" by Pink and "I’m Every Woman" by Whitney Houston. Watch That’s My Jam, Mondays 9/8c on NBC.

ABOUT THAT’S MY JAM
Hosted by Jimmy Fallon, “That’s My Jam” is an hour long music and comedy variety game show that draws inspiration from the most popular “Tonight Show” games. Each episode features two teams of two celebrities competing for a charity of their choice in a series of music, dance, and trivia-based games and musical performances. Signature games to be played include Launch the Mic, Air Guitar, Don’t Drop the Beat, Perfect Mash-Up, Wheel of Impossible Karaoke, Slay It, Don’t Spray It and many more.

The format was brought to Universal Television Alternative Studio by Fallon, longtime “The Tonight Show” producer Jim Juvonen and writer Josh Knapp. Adam Blackstone is Musical Director and will lead the house band throughout each episode. Mike Yurchuk will serve as showrunner.

lPtwBJyC21I.description:
Normani sings a countrified version of “Creep” by TLC in this unpredictable game of Musical Genre Challenge. Watch That’s My Jam, Mondays 9/8c on NBC.

ABOUT THAT’S MY JAM
Hosted by Jimmy Fallon, “That’s My Jam” is an hour long music and comedy variety game show that draws inspiration from the most popular “Tonight Show” games. Each episode features two teams of two celebrities competing for a charity of their choice in a series of music, dance, and trivia-based games and musical performances. Signature games to be played include Launch the Mic, Air Guitar, Don’t Drop the Beat, Perfect Mash-Up, Wheel of Impossible Karaoke, Slay It, Don’t Spray It and many more.

The format was brought to Universal Television Alternative Studio by Fallon, longtime “The Tonight Show” producer Jim Juvonen and writer Josh Knapp. Adam Blackstone is Musical Director and will lead the house band throughout each episode. Mike Yurchuk will serve as showrunner.

ABOUT THAT’S MY JAM
Hosted by Jimmy Fallon, “That’s My Jam” is an hourlong music and comedy variety game show that draws inspiration from the most popular “Tonight Show” games. Each episode features two teams of two celebrities competing for a charity of their choice in a series of music, dance, and trivia-based games and musical performances. Signature games to be played include Launch the Mic, Air Guitar, Don’t Drop the Beat, Perfect Mash-Up, Wheel of Impossible Karaoke, Slay It, Don’t Spray It and many more.

The format was brought to Universal Television Alternative Studio by Fallon, longtime “The Tonight Show” producer Jim Juvonen and writer Josh Knapp. Adam Blackstone is Musical Director and will lead the house band throughout each episode. Mike Yurchuk will serve as showrunner.

The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon presents this exclusive trailer for Martin Scorsese's The Irishman, starring Robert De Niro, Al Pacino, and Joe Pesci. The Irishman hits theaters November 1 and on Netflix November 27.

Connect with The Irishman Online
FOLLOW The Irishman on Twitter: https://twitter.com/theirishmanfilm
FOLLOW The Irishman on Instagram: https://instagram.com/theirishmanfilm
LIKE The Irishman on Facebook: https://facebook.com/theirishmanfilm
 
Robert De Niro, Al Pacino and Joe Pesci star in Martin Scorsese's THE IRISHMAN, an epic saga of organized crime in post-war America told through the eyes of World War II veteran Frank Sheeran, a hustler and hitman who worked alongside some of the most notorious figures of the 20th century. Spanning decades, the film chronicles one of the greatest unsolved mysteries in American history, the disappearance of legendary union boss Jimmy Hoffa, and offers a monumental journey through the hidden corridors of organized crime: its inner workings, rivalries and connections to mainstream politics.
